{"tid":1037801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉殺子被控謀殺 母親今缺席聆訊稍後轉往青山醫院","createTime":"2019-02-26T07:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T11:34:07.000Z","uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c43632a44919f06262848b9b895c99c7d9b3d088","tid":1037801,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T07:48:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190226/59304693\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190226%2F59304693&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=b1affc18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190226%2F59304693&h=567136b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190226/59304693</a><br />\n痴鳩線老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nR.I.P"},{"pid":"de9328b50fee4dd90f10d84d210b3fdc925dd276","tid":1037801,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T07:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a19491e8673ed27ec651aede2dee649d7743a40","tid":1037801,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T07:49:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190226/59304693\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190226%2F59304693&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=b1affc18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190226%2F59304693&h=567136b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190226/59304693</a><br />\n將軍澳善明邨日前發生倫常慘案，55歲母親涉殺死23歲兒子，其後自殺不遂。涉案母親被控一項謀殺罪，案件今於觀塘裁判法院提訊。涉案母親缺席聆訊，控方指她現仍在將軍澳醫院留醫，相信今日稍後會轉往青山醫院。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官將案件押後至下月4日再訊，並詢問控方會否索閱被告的精神科報告，控方稱會考慮，又指被告若提早出院，會盡早將她押解上庭。<br />\n<br />\n報稱是清潔工的被告趙麗霞，被指於本月22日（上周五）在將軍澳善明邨善裕樓住處內謀殺兒子。<br />\n痴鳩線老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nR.I.P</blockquote>"},{"pid":"19d6f230d0bb85ec9c16c10528973f22419766c7","tid":1037801,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T07:51:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30543a0f3fab2f44fa9a4e84e0bbe7f42e673ac","tid":1037801,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T11:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db65523afb2661522331676c714aad79dd81c19","tid":1037801,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T11:34:07.000Z","msg":"個老母痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}